# Coding Standards — Hana CMS

> Source of truth cho style: `biome.json` (root).
> **Khi đổi biome config → cập nhật file này.**

## Formatting (Biome v2)

```
indent:      2 spaces (KHÔNG tabs)
quotes:      single (')
semicolons:  asNeeded — KHÔNG có semicolon cuối dòng
lineWidth:   100 characters
```

Ví dụ đúng:

```typescript
// ✅ no semicolons, single quotes, 2-space indent
import type { CMSPlugin } from '@hanano/types'

export function createPlugin(name: string): CMSPlugin {
  return {
    name,
    version: '1.0.0',
  }
}
```

## TypeScript

### Export style

```typescript
// ✅ Named exports trong packages (KHÔNG default export)
export class HanaCMS { ... }
export function createCMS(config: CMSConfig): HanaCMS { ... }
export type { CMSConfig, CMSPlugin }

// ❌ Tránh default export trong packages/
export default HanaCMS
```

### Type imports

```typescript
// ✅ Dùng import type khi chỉ cần type
import type { CMSPlugin, CMSConfig } from '@hanano/types'
import type { Hono } from 'hono'

// ✅ Import value khi cần runtime
import { Hono } from 'hono'
import { drizzle } from 'drizzle-orm/libsql'
```

### Error handling

```typescript
// ✅ Throw với context cụ thể
throw new Error(`Database driver "${config.driver}" is not yet supported. Use "sqlite".`)
throw new Error(`Schema conflict: table "${key}" is defined by multiple plugins.`)

// ✅ Async error handling
async function fetchData() {
  try {
    const data = await someAsyncOperation()
    return data
  } catch (error) {
    throw new Error(`fetchData failed: ${error instanceof Error ? error.message : String(error)}`)
  }
}

// ❌ Empty catch, swallow errors
try { ... } catch (_) { }
```

### Async patterns

```typescript
// ✅ async/await
const result = await cms.launch()

// ❌ .then() chains
cms.launch().then(app => ...).catch(err => ...)
```

### Naming conventions

```
Variables/functions:  camelCase    (createDatabase, hookRegistry)
Classes:              PascalCase   (HanaCMS, HookRegistry, PluginRegistryClient)
Interfaces/Types:     PascalCase   (CMSPlugin, DatabaseConfig)
Constants:            UPPER_SNAKE  (MAX_RETRY_COUNT) — chỉ cho true constants
Files:                kebab-case   (hook-registry.ts, schema-builder.ts)
Directories:          kebab-case   (plugin-auth/, packages/core/)
```

### `noExplicitAny`

Biome config: `noExplicitAny: "warn"` — cố gắng tránh `any`, dùng `unknown` và narrow type:

```typescript
// ✅ Dùng unknown + type guard
function process(value: unknown) {
  if (typeof value === 'string') { ... }
}

// ⚠️ Cần có comment lý do nếu phải dùng any
const handler = handler as (...a: unknown[]) => unknown  // HookRegistry internal
```

## File Organization (trong mỗi package)

```
packages/core/src/
├── index.ts           ← re-export public API
├── hana-cms.ts        ← main class
├── hook-registry.ts   ← HookRegistry
└── database.ts        ← createDatabase()
```

- `index.ts` chỉ re-export, không có logic
- Mỗi file có **1 responsibility chính**
- File không vượt quá ~150 lines (nếu quá → tách module)

## Vue (apps/admin)

```vue
<!-- ✅ script setup syntax -->
<script setup lang="ts">
import { ref } from 'vue'
const count = ref(0)
</script>

<template>
  <div>{{ count }}</div>
</template>
```

- Dùng `<script setup>` (Composition API), KHÔNG Options API
- Component names: PascalCase (`AdminLayout.vue`, `PluginsView.vue`)

